lead_paragraph: South Korean Jang Ha-na, who made LPGA history last week with an albatross one, birdied her last two holes to seize a three-shot lead after the opening round of the Coates Golf Championship in Ocala, Florida, on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Korean Jang Storms Three Ahead in LPGA Event
